{
  "name": "皇帝模拟器",
  "description": "",
  "first_mes": "「天镜阁」前的铜铃随风轻响，一卷泛黄的天命图录在案上缓缓展开。\n\n你即将踏入的不是寻常话本，而是一场可以亲手改写的历朝兴衰。或为九五之尊执掌乾坤，或为名臣良将匡扶社稷，或为江湖游侠快意恩仇——每一次朱笔落下，都可能掀起蝴蝶效应，令史书上的既定轨迹悄然偏转。\n\n殿外更漏沉沉，内侍已备好冕旒与玉玺。山河万里，黎庶亿兆，皆在等你第一道旨意。\n\n<StatusPlaceHolderImpl/>",
  "creatorcomment": "皇帝模拟器 · 天镜阁沙盒文字RPG",
  "data": {
    "name": "皇帝模拟器",
    "description": "",
    "first_mes": "「天镜阁」前的铜铃随风轻响，一卷泛黄的天命图录在案上缓缓展开。\n\n你即将踏入的不是寻常话本，而是一场可以亲手改写的历朝兴衰。或为九五之尊执掌乾坤，或为名臣良将匡扶社稷，或为江湖游侠快意恩仇——每一次朱笔落下，都可能掀起蝴蝶效应，令史书上的既定轨迹悄然偏转。\n\n殿外更漏沉沉，内侍已备好冕旒与玉玺。山河万里，黎庶亿兆，皆在等你第一道旨意。\n\n<StatusPlaceHolderImpl/>",
    "creator_notes": "皇帝模拟器 · 天镜阁沙盒文字RPG",
    "creator": "huangdimoniqi",
    "character_version": "1.0.0",
    "alternate_greetings": [],
    "extensions": {
      "world": "皇帝模拟器",
      "regex_scripts": [
        {
          "id": "huangdi-strip-update",
          "scriptName": "[不发送]去除变量更新",
          "disabled": false,
          "runOnEdit": false,
          "findRegex": "/<update(?:variable)?>(?:(?!.*<\\/update(?:variable)?>).*$|.*<\\/update(?:variable)?>)/gsi",
          "replaceString": "",
          "trimStrings": [],
          "placement": [
            1,
            2
          ],
          "substituteRegex": 0,
          "minDepth": null,
          "maxDepth": 3,
          "markdownOnly": false,
          "promptOnly": true
        },
        {
          "id": "huangdi-fold-update-pending",
          "scriptName": "[折叠]变量更新中",
          "disabled": false,
          "runOnEdit": false,
          "findRegex": "/<update(?:variable)?>(?!.*<\\/update(?:variable)?>)\\s*(.*)\\s*$/gsi",
          "replaceString": "\n<details>\n<summary>变量更新中{{random::.::..::...}}</summary>\n$1\n</details>",
          "trimStrings": [],
          "placement": [
            1,
            2
          ],
          "substituteRegex": 0,
          "minDepth": null,
          "maxDepth": null,
          "markdownOnly": true,
          "promptOnly": false
        },
        {
          "id": "huangdi-fold-update-done",
          "scriptName": "[折叠]完整变量更新",
          "disabled": false,
          "runOnEdit": false,
          "findRegex": "/<update(?:variable)?>\\s*(.*)\\s*<\\/update(?:variable)?>/gsi",
          "replaceString": "\n<details>\n<summary>变量更新情况</summary>\n$1\n</details>",
          "trimStrings": [],
          "placement": [
            1,
            2
          ],
          "substituteRegex": 0,
          "minDepth": null,
          "maxDepth": null,
          "markdownOnly": true,
          "promptOnly": false
        },
        {
          "id": "huangdi-iframe-ui",
          "scriptName": "[界面]皇帝模拟器",
          "disabled": false,
          "runOnEdit": false,
          "findRegex": "<StatusPlaceHolderImpl/>",
          "replaceString": "```\n<body>\n<script>\n$('body').load('http://127.0.0.1:5500/huangdimoniqi/界面/模拟器/index.html')\n</script>\n</body>\n```",
          "trimStrings": [],
          "placement": [
            2
          ],
          "substituteRegex": 0,
          "minDepth": null,
          "maxDepth": null,
          "markdownOnly": true,
          "promptOnly": false
