        {
          "id": 3,
          "keys": [],
          "secondary_keys": [],
          "comment": "[mvu_update]变量更新规则",
          "content": "---\n变量更新规则:\n  游戏:\n    历法:\n      check:\n        - 时间推进、重大事件后更新古代历法描述\n    地点:\n      check:\n        - 角色移动、驾临新场所时更新\n    天气:\n      type: |-\n        {\n          名称: string;\n          描述: string;\n          图标: string;\n        }\n      check:\n        - 季节更替、灾害或剧情需要时更新\n  角色:\n    attributes:\n      type: |-\n        {\n          health: number;\n          prestige: number;\n          gold: number;\n          military: number;\n          defense: number;\n          strength: number;\n          agility: number;\n          stamina: number;\n          intelligence: number;\n          luck: number;\n        }\n      check:\n        - 重大决策、战斗、册封、赈灾等事件后合理调整\n        - health/prestige/military/defense 单次变化通常不超过 ±15\n        - 核心属性 strength 等单次变化通常不超过 ±0.5\n    background:\n      check:\n        - 仅在身份、经历发生重大变化时更新\n  帝国:\n    summary:\n      check:\n        - 天下大势变化时更新朝政概况\n    treasury:\n      type: number\n      check:\n        - 赈灾、战争、税收、赏赐后更新\n    sentiment:\n      type: number\n      range: 0~100\n      check:\n        - 仁政、暴政、天灾人祸后调整民望\n    military:\n      type: number\n      check:\n        - 征兵、战败、边防变动后更新\n    grain:\n      type: number\n      check:\n        - 丰收、饥荒、赈济后更新\n  任务:\n    type: |-\n      {\n        [任务编号: string]: {\n          title: string;\n          description: string;\n          status: '进行中' | '已达成' | '已失败';\n          type: '主线' | '支线' | '奇遇';\n          reward: string;\n        }\n      }\n    check:\n      - 剧情触发新使命时 insert，完成或失败后 replace status\n  物品:\n    type: |-\n      {\n        [物品编号: string]: {\n          name: string;\n          description: string;\n          quality: '神传' | '绝世' | '奇珍' | '凡器';\n          type: string;\n          count: number;\n        }\n      }\n    check:\n      - 获得、消耗、赏赐物品时更新；count 归零后 remove\n  技能:\n    type: |-\n      {\n        [技能编号: string]: {\n          name: string;\n          level: string;\n          description: string;\n          exp: number;\n          type: string;\n        }\n      }\n    check:\n      - 修炼、顿悟、传授后更新 exp 或 level\n  NPC:\n    type: |-\n      {\n        [人物编号: string]: {\n          name: string;\n          role: string;\n          relationship: string;\n          relationVal: number;\n          loyalty: number;\n          statusText: string;\n        }\n      }\n    check:\n      - 人物登场、关系变化、忠诚度变动时更新\n  编年:\n    type: |-\n      Array<{\n        turn: number;\n        year: number;\n        eventText: string;\n      }>\n    check:\n      - 重大历史事件后以 insert 追加，保留最近 20 条\n  当前剧情:\n    story:\n      check:\n        - 由模拟器界面主导演算，聊天中通常不直接覆盖\n    worldEvent:\n      check:\n        - 天下大势播报，随剧情推进更新",
          "constant": true,
          "selective": false,
          "insertion_order": 14720,
